resources.string: This application helps to manage and plan nice events by provides a list of various venues that match your requirements and also provides the other details about those venues like location,ratings,reviews, contact details.\nFor venue manager/vendors it provides admin signup to enlist their venues in this application to increase their customers.\n This application also provides the list of services/amenities that could be used with specific event.
